item.title: CVE-2017-1445|2024-08-05T13:32:29.645Z -- ibm -- emptoris%20spend%20analysis
item.description: IBM Emptoris Spend Analysis 9.5.0.0 through 10.1.1 is vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 128170.
